column1: \ The following lines define the label and column names correspondance.
\ Spectral Type                                      = Spectral_Type   =  defsp +- defspe + defsplim
\ Calculated Luminosity                              = L_solar         =  deflum +- deflume + deflumlim
\ Calculated Effective Temperatures                  = Teff_theory     =  defcteff +- defcteffe + defctefflim
\ Distance or Parallax                               = Distance        =  defdist +- defdiste + defplxlim
\ PM in right ascension                              = PMra            =  defpmra +- defpmrae + defpmralim
\ PM in declination                                  = PMDec           =  defpmdec +- defpmdece + defpmdeclim
\ Include systems with known planets                 = Planets         =  defnplanet
\ Habitable zone inner radius                        = HZ_inner        =  defhzinarad
\ Habitable zone outer radius                        = HZ_outer        =  defhzoutarad
\ Predicted Earth-like transit depth                 = Transit_Depth_Earth =  defertdpv
\ Predicted radial velocity wobble from Earth        = RV_Wobble_Earth =  defertrvelw
\ Predicted astrometric wobble from Earth            = Ast_Wobble_Earth =  defertposw
\ Predicted Jupiter-like transit depth               = Transit_Depth_Jovian =  defjupdpv
\ Predicted radial velocity wobble from Jupiter      = RV_Wobble_Jovian =  defjuprvelw
\ Predicted astrometric wobble from Jupiter          = Ast_Wobble_Jovian =  defjupposw
\ defpmra   : Default proper motion in ra
\ defpmrae  : Default error in proper motion in ra
\ defpmralim: Default ra proper motion limit flag
\ defpmdec  : Default proper motion in dec
\ defpmdece : Default error in proper motion in dec
\ defpmdeclim: Default dec proper motion limit flag
\ defbjlim  : Default B-band magnitude limit flag
\ defvjlim  : Default V-band magnitude limit flag
\ defklim   : Default K-band (2Mass) magnitude limit flag
\ defspe    : Default spectral type error string
\ defsplim  : Default spectral type limit flag
\ defctefflim: Default Computed Teff limit flag
\ deflumlim : Default Computed Luminosity limit flag
\ defhzinarad: Default inner habitable zone angular radius
\ defhzoutarad: Default outer habitable zone angular radius
\ defertrvelw: Default Earth radial velocity kick (m/s)
\ defertdpv : Default Earth primary transity depth at V (ratio)
\ defjuprvelw: Default Jupiter radial velocity kick (m/s)
\ defjupdpv : Default Jupiter primary transity depth at V (ratio)
\ defnaxa   : Number of AXA light curves
